text: Alejandro Eduardo Giammattei Falla (born 9 March 1956) is a Guatemalan politician. He was the President of Guatemala from 14 January 2020 until 14 January 2024. He was elected president after winning the second round of the 2019 presidential election. He was a candidate for President in the 2007, 2011, 2015, and 2019 elections. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Guatemala Category:People from Guatemala City Category:People with multiple sclerosis
